Chromatic Jaran Cavalry was created/rendered by Thobie Buntaran a.k.a. Loreng on 24 November 2020, Mantrijeron, Yogyakarta, Indonesia.

A good companion for digital “Kurukshetra” war in the future, but for now he’s just grazing around the Santuari.
